1
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:17,680
Girls,

2
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,080
VIP Room V8 is full of important guests.

3
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:21,760
When you go in later,

4
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,000
be on your best behavior.

5
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:24,440
Do you hear me?

6
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,480
Yes.

7
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,280
Tianyan,

8
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:30,360
what's wrong with you?

9
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:31,200
Come here.

10
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:39,000
Today, the Silver Light Hall is trading.

11
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:41,280
The head of the family, Pang Jingfu, is very dangerous.

12
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:43,480
[You must hide yourself well,]

13
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:45,120
[and don't draw his attention.]

14
00:00:45,640 --> 00:00:46,920
[Don't worry, Master.]

15
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:49,760
[I've been undercover in IPCO for years.]

16
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,640
[I've saved enough money.]

17
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,800
[After this mission,]

18
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,840
[I'll retire and go back to school.]

19
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,000
[It wasn't until much later]

20
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,200
[that I finally realized]

21
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:06,920
[that night,]

22
00:01:07,440 --> 00:01:08,880
[I walked through a door]

23
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:13,600
[that I could never escape from.]

24
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,280
Bastard!

25
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:35,080
I'm so sorry!

26
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,440
I know I was wrong!

27
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,760
I'll never do it again!

28
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,680
Please spare my life!

29
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,560
Impressive!

30
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,440
Dare to betray Brother Fu?

31
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,200
Do you know what will happen to you?

32
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,960
I'm sorry, but it's not like that.

33
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,960
I was blinded by their money.

34
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,400
Please forgive me.

35
00:01:57,240 --> 00:01:58,440
Please, spare my life.

36
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,560
Surprise!

37
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,000
You've been here for two years,

38
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,840
and you still don't know the rules?

39
00:02:11,040 --> 00:02:12,640
Why meddle in other people's business?

40
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,400
Take her away.

41
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,080
What are you looking at?

42
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,040
Well, we came up here

43
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,000
to bring some wine

44
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,040
to liven up the party.

45
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,120
We're all new here.

46
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,320
New here,

47
00:02:52,640 --> 00:02:53,920
so you think you can disregard the rules?

48
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,440
Do you also want to die

49
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,680
for daring to look me in the eye?

50
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:59,040
I'm sorry.

51
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,320
Anyone who enters Mr. Fu's private room for the first time

52
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,840
must kneel to enter,

53
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,520
to humble them.

54
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,640
Will you kneel or not?

55
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:24,520
Come here.

56
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,600
Mr. Fu,

57
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,080
the new girl is inexperienced.

58
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,120
I'll replace her right away.

59
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,960
Don't you get out of here?

60
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:36,200
Brother Fu said to let her go over there.

61
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:38,000
Can't you understand?

62
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,880
Mr. Fu,

63
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:02,960
your wine.

64
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,000
You've got some guts,

65
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,880
and you're quite skilled.

66
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,480
Mr. Fu,

67
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,160
please...

68
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:30,880
I...

69
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,160
I'm just trying to

70
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,960
pay off my parents' debts

71
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,920
and make some money.

72
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,920
Mr. Fu, please don't!

73
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,480
Mr. Fu!

74
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,240
Mr. Fu!

75
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:47,920
Please.

76
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:49,920
Please.

77
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,080
Mr. Fu.

78
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,600
Don't.

79
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,960
Mr. Fu, don't.

80
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,480
Don't.

81
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,280
You haven't done anything yet,

82
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,240
and you've already shown your true colors.

83
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,520
You must be tired of living.

84
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,400
Take them all away.

85
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,080
Hurry up.

86
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,640
You...

87
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,640
Hurry up!

88
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,600
Manager,

89
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,440
please save that new girl.

90
00:05:30,640 --> 00:05:32,360
She's locked up in Box 888.

91
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,720
What's wrong with you, Zhu Ruoyun?

92
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,800
Even if she's killed today,

93
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,240
no one would dare say a word.

94
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:42,560
Qi,

95
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,120
don't be so rude.

96
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:50,760
What's your name?

97
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,760
Tian Yan.

98
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,520
So touching.

99
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:04,080
He's willing to sacrifice his life for you.

100
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,520
I don't know him.

101
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,440
Please don't kill me.

102
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:14,560
You think I'm a softie?

103
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:19,600
I just believe

104
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,400
you wouldn't wrong an innocent person.

105
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:29,480
Take her back.

106
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,800
I'll interrogate him myself.

107
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,360
If you want to pretend,

108
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,000
pretend thoroughly.

109
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,800
Otherwise, you don't even deserve to be a dog.

110
00:06:58,280 --> 00:06:59,560
It's dangerous here.

111
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,800
I just want to survive.

112
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,080
Then it seems I owe you an apology.

113
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,080
Brother Fu,

114
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:18,640
there are killers.

115
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,240
Go.

116
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,240
Where will they take Master?

117
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,640
Then go back.

118
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,840
I'll interrogate them myself.

119
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,280
Go back?

120
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,320
To his home?

121
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:40,800
Mr. Fu.

122
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,120
Mr. Fu.

123
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:50,680
Save me.

124
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,600
They're trying to kill me.

125
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,520
Please protect me.

126
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,000
Brother Fu.

127
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,160
Drive.

128
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,920
Take him home.

129
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,360
Why is it...

130
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,160
Take him to my home?

131
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,440
What should I do?

132
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,080
Master is still in his hands.

133
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,400
Mr. Fu.

134
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,520
Thank you.

135
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,160
You're leaving?

136
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,520
You're...

137
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,680
Inviting me

138
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:31,960
to your house?

139
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,920
No, no, no.

140
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:34,720
I...

141
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:40,520
Take care.

142
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,200
Goodbye.

143
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,920
Tan Sunxun,

144
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,560
is this what you call

145
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,680
the third wheel?

146
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,200
I know you're playing the role of

147
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,480
a white flower paying off debts,

148
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:39,040
but you look

149
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:40,680
a bit worn out,

150
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,320
my junior sister.

151
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,680
No time for jokes.

152
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:46,320
Master was captured by Pang Jingfu

153
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,440
while trying to save me.

154
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:49,920
What?

155
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,800
He should be

156
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:54,240
locked up in his mansion.

157
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:56,400
His mansion?

158
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,200
That's the Silver Light Hall's stronghold.

159
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,000
I tried to follow him,

160
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,640
but he

161
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,440
sent me home.

162
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,280
Didn't Pang Jingfu suspect you?

163
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,600
See you.

164
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,200
I can't see through him.

165
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,960
Brother Fu,

166
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,600
the killers

167
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,880
seem to be Young Master Fan's men.

168
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:39,960
Isn't he abroad?

169
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:41,880
No way.

170
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:45,400
My brother has been a loser since childhood.

171
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:49,440
Otherwise, how could this bastard become head?

172
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,400
Although

173
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,800
I retired early,

174
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:54,800
I'm

175
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,040
not blind.

176
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,320
Brother Fu,

177
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,000
you are capable and shrewd.

178
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,320
If others want to take over,

179
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,960
they are daydreaming.

180
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,720
How is that manager?

181
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,600
We've tried everything,

182
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,160
he still

183
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,680
didn't say a word.

184
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:14,000
That proves his identity.

185
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:16,640
But Brother Fu,

186
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,680
you're really something.

187
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,600
You personally sent that girl home.

188
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,880
To be a scapegoat.

189
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:23,800
Hurry.

190
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,440
Pang Jingfu's car is here.

191
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:32,600
He must still be upstairs.

192
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:32,920
Go!

193
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:33,280
Go!

194
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:39,560
Wait.

195
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:41,760
Pang Jingfu is being hunted.

196
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,520
He won't be kind enough

197
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,280
to send you home.

198
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:35,560
You go first.

199
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,520
I'll cover you.

200
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:14,520
Mr. Fu.

201
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,080
Mr. Fu.

202
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,960
Please save me.

203
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:00,840
Mom...

204
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,160
Liyou,

205
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,920
I can do anything you want me to do,

206
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:14,800
as long as you're willing to take me in.

207
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:31,400
I told you,

208
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:34,080
you don't even have the right to be a dog.

209
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,000
Mr. Fu, please.

210
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,840
The killers from the club have followed me home.

211
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,320
I really have nowhere to go.

212
00:16:41,560 --> 00:16:43,040
Please take me in.

213
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,360
I'm begging you, Mr. Fu.
